Third-Party Runtime Notice

Documentation baseline for this notice: HyperTool v2.3.5.

HyperTool can optionally integrate with external runtime dependencies that are
maintained outside this repository and are distributed under their own licenses:

- usbipd-win (Host USB runtime): https://github.com/dorssel/usbipd-win
- usbip-win2 (Guest USB runtime): https://github.com/vadimgrn/usbip-win2
- WinFsp (Guest shared-folder runtime): https://github.com/winfsp/winfsp

Their copyright and license terms are defined by the respective upstream
projects and remain unaffected by HyperTool's MIT license.
